' ==========================================
' 顶层依赖与组合关系
' ==========================================
BaseSimulation *-- CelestialEnvironment
BaseSimulation *-- SpacecraftPointMass
BaseSimulation *-- GroundStation
BaseSimulation *-- GNC_Subsystem
BaseSimulation *-- HDF5Logger
BaseSimulation ..> BaseTrajectoryGenerator : 使用工厂创建生成器
ThreeBodyBaseSimulation o-- CRTBP

@enduml